profile: Providing permanent solutions to homeowners with wet basements, musty crawl spaces, bowing or settling foundations. Full line of sump pumps and dehumidifiers. Certified Radon Gas Mitigator. Solid, thorough service to our customers is the #1 priority and we stand behind our work with written warranties! Fully staffed to start and finish your project on time as expected with the best products in the industry. We hold over 28 patented products, have won the BBB Integrity Award and do not sub-contract our core business. Family owned by Martin & Julie Bates
service_area: All of South Western Ontario including Goderich and surrounding area.
products: Drainage, sump liners, sump pump systems, radon gas test kits, radon gas mitigation systems, dehumidifiers, encapsulation systems, crawl space jacks, crawl space doors, crawl space beam/joist repair, wall anchors, wall braces, concrete lifting/leveling, basement flooring.
services: Complete basement waterproofing, crawl space encapsulation and wood repair, radon gas testing and mitigation, bowing wall repair, helical/push piers, concrete slab lifting, foundation rebuilds.
brands: Zoeller, Apriaire, Basement Systems, Clean Space, Total Basement Finishing, Foundation Supportworks
diplomas: Certified Waterproofing Specialist, Certified Crawl Space Specialist
memberships: BBB, Home Builder's Association, Chamber of Commerce, CERTI, CFIB
